featured_reviews.review_id:
The mosque is a place of prayer for Muslims and remains accessible at all hours for Namaz. I am pleased to let you know that anybody is welcome to offer Namaz in such a peaceful environment at Allah's home. I'm at a loss for words to adequately express the beauty of this mosque. You are cordially invited to visit for a better experience, and I also pray that Almighty Allah encourages everyone to offer salah. Remember me in Duas, JazakAllah.

With Regards,
Dr. Mohd Irshad
Researcher (Department of Plant Protection)
Aligarh Muslim University, Aligarh - 202002
